Atrium OpenTok
=======================
-Provides integration with OpenTok's Video Chat API.
-Allows groups to have broadcast or group chat sessions.

Requirements:
-OpenTokAPI: https://github.com/markwk/opentokapi (Drupal 6 Helper Module)
-Libraries module: http://drupal.org/project/libraries 
-Libraries:
    1. jquery.opentok: https://github.com/markwk/jquery-opentok  => rename directory to: jquery.opentok
    2. jquery.resize: https://github.com/cowboy/jquery-resize => rename directory to: jquery.resize
    3. json-js: https://github.com/douglascrockford/JSON-js => rename directory to: json-js

Installation:
 1. Add the necessary depenencies in the sites/all/libraries directory
 2. Enable Feature
 3. Add Your OpenTok Developer's Keys from http://www.tokbox.com/opentok/api
 4. Enable within desired group
 5. Create a Video Chat, enable as broadcast or group chat

Problems? Add it to the Issue Queue: https://github.com/markwk/atrium_opentok/issues

